profile:
Groundbreaking Landscapes offers full-service landscape construction for Saskatoon and area. We specialize in sprinklers and irrigation, hardscape patios and walkways, topsoil and sod installations. We Are a company that values our customers and want to fulfill all of their requests and needs. As a smaller company, you can expect that the owner will be on site working with the crew. We want to help YOU create a yard that you can be proud of and enjoy for years to come!

Check us out at Groundbreakinglandscapes.ca or Groundbreaking Landscapes on Instagram or Facebook for picture and reviews of the work we do!

We do creative landscaping, design and maintenance, stonework, paving stone patios, walkways and driveways, retaining walls, tree and shrub pruning.
We also sell real stone flagstone, feature stones, and gravel. Residential, commercial, acreages,- we do it all.
We are members of the Saskatchewan and Canadian Nursery Landscape Association
